stories.text:
Guys, have you ever heard about successful SaaS presale? I've read some articles about it and comparisons to Tesla's Cybertruck (duh), but there was never any serious scale involved, more like a dozen seats sold. What would encourage you personally to invest like this? Is it lifetime access or money back guarantee? What is the max price that you'll pay for MarTech tool on a presale terms?
Thank you for all of your feedback in advance! :)
stories.title: SaaS Presale – Opportunity or Scam?

stories.text:
So, we’ve all heard of Doge and Shiba Inu, and my wife and I have decided that we want to create our own memecoin. This is just for personal use, no actual monetary value.

But I haven’t been able to find much documentation on how to do this sort of thing, or links to sites or services that can make this happen.

Which also leads me to believe that maybe we could start up a business helping others to do this sort of thing?

Anyway, what sites or resources am I missing?
stories.title: Ask HN: How do you create your own meme coin?
